1
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:14,320
We shouldn't stay here long.

2
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:16,280
Let's go.

3
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:18,600
Let's go.

4
00:00:26,560 --> 00:00:27,440
Ayu,

5
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,960
calm down.

6
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:30,160
If Su Cheng is being framed,

7
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,320
then you are being used.

8
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:32,759
The evidence is irrefutable.

9
00:00:32,759 --> 00:00:34,280
Don't be fooled by him.

10
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:45,640
What's going on?

11
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:47,880
Jiuyun,

12
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,450
I won't hurt you.

13
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,840
Su Cheng,

14
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:56,080
there really is something wrong with you.

15
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:57,560
Thinking I would just surrender

16
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,080
is your problem.

17
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:02,160
These are my secretly trained assassins.

18
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,840
Today, for Jiuyun's sake...

19
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,440
I'll spare your life for now.

20
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:06,760
Let's go.

21
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:11,640
Don't you want to know the truth?

22
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:12,600
Come with me.

23
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:39,200
Don't worry. Next,

24
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:41,720
it's time to close the net.

25
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:48,520
It seems these death squads are Su Cheng's last trump card.

26
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:52,320
Assemble the imperial guards immediately

27
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,640
and arrest him.

28
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:56,880
Sir, you supported me to become the God of War

29
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:59,160
and gave me evidence to convict Su Cheng.

30
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,720
You took so much trouble.

31
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,580
What is your real purpose?

32
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,920
You dare to question me?

33
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,720
You are the one who wants revenge

34
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:13,400
and to win back Mu Jiuyun.

35
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:16,560
Yun would never favor Su Cheng for no reason.

36
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:20,040
Is Su Cheng really the murderer?

37
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:22,440
Or was Su Cheng

38
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,480
framed by you?

39
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,960
If getting rid of Su Cheng

40
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,960
can help you win back Mu Jiuyun,

41
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,160
does the truth

42
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,920
really matter?

43
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,160
Yes, it does.

44
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:44,680
Why did you train death squads?

45
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:47,540
What does the murder of the envoy have to do with you?

46
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,440
I'm getting more and more confused.

47
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,520
Do you hope

48
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,840
I have something to do with this,

49
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,040
or nothing to do with it?

50
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,079
Stop smiling.

51
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,200
I'm being serious.

52
00:02:58,320 --> 00:03:00,080
I promise you,

53
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,320
I'm not the killer.

54
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:02,800
As for the death squads,

55
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,860
they are my trump card to save my life.

56
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,280
I knew it.

57
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,340
Su Cheng knows who the mastermind is.

58
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,360
What are you going to do now?

59
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,079
Right now, all I want

60
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:18,690
is to take you away from all this plotting.

61
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:24,960
Seeking the truth comes with a price.

62
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,600
Jiuyun, trust me.

63
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,079
Knowing nothing

64
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:32,560
is the best choice for you.

65
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,600
I bought a piece of land in the suburbs.

66
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,800
No one knows about it.

67
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,040
We can spend the rest of our lives there,

68
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,880
okay?

69
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,840
Su Cheng.

70
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,240
I saved you,

71
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,900
but it doesn't mean I like you.

72
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:50,160
And you have no right to make choices for me.

73
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:52,240
If ten years ago,

74
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,280
I hadn't left you,

75
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,570
would things be different between us now?

76
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,120
Ten years...

77
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,640
A lot has changed.

78
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:06,120
It's all that damn shadow's fault.

79
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,240
Su Cheng.

80
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:12,560
I only see you as a childhood friend.

81
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:18,240
A'yu and I are true lovers.

82
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,200
If you insist on this,

83
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,280
we will be enemies from now on.

84
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,120
What are you doing?

85
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,640
Going to find the truth.

86
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,730
The truth is important.

87
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,650
If Su Cheng is really the true culprit,

88
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,200
I will definitely bring him to justice.

89
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:50,760
I think you are addicted to being this shadow god of war.

90
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,800
Punishing evil is not your duty.

91
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,520
Don't forget your purpose.

92
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,680
I haven't forgotten.

93
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,370
But if I kill the innocent indiscriminately,

94
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:05,260
Ayun will definitely not forgive me.

95
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,800
I see.

96
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:16,680
You would rather believe Mu Jiuyun, who is being played by Su Cheng,

97
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:21,920
than believe me who provides evidence.

98
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,850
I haven't even seen your true face.

99
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,560
How can I trust you?

100
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,480
Okay.

101
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:33,960
Then I'll let you see.

102
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:40,880
Go,

103
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,880
bring the true culprit back.

104
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,760
Where are we?

105
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:07,820
Didn't you want to find the truth?

106
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,360
This is the enemy spy base.

107
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,880
Once we find their leader,

108
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,940
we'll know who is giving them orders,

109
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,180
and exactly who is trying to frame me.

110
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,360
What are we waiting for then?

111
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,200
Don't rush.

112
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,840
My lord, there is no one inside.

113
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:26,920
What?

114
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,680
My lord, nothing.

115
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,200
My lord, there is no one here.

116
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,240
Why is there no one here?

117
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,720
Is the intel wrong?

118
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:44,050
Obviously, someone was here not long ago.

119
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,480
Go search again,

120
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,960
and see if there are any clues.

121
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,640
Yes, sir.

122
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,040
Su Cheng,

123
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,560
you really are the spy leader.

124
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,200
Absolutely impossible.

125
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,170
We just arrived.

126
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:04,490
Su Cheng, the evidence is conclusive.

127
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,160
Take him away.

128
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,200
Move.

129
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,480
If I die,

130
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,540
bury me under the yellow flower tree.

131
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,880
Go.

132
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,080
Hurry.

133
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,520
Yun.

134
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:41,890
Bo Baorui

135
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:45,700
Zhong Xiaqiang

136
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:46,900
Pengyin

137
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:47,320
Zijian Qiangqipin Pengyin

138
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,340
Zijian Qiangqipin

139
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:48,600
Quan Xuhang

140
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,260
Quan Xuhang

141
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:49,920
Quan Yulong

142
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,580
Quan Yulong

143
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,600
Licheng Lefei

144
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,040
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing

145
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:56,880
Luoxiao Conglin Xunbo
